<h2>Objective</h2>
<p>
Assess academic administrative workflows for clarity, consistency,
and operational effectiveness.
</p>

<h2>Key Findings</h2>
<ul>
<li>Department workflows varied significantly</li>
<li>Manual processes created delays</li>
<li>Approval steps were not consistently documented</li>
</ul>

<h2>Recommendations</h2>
<ul>
<li>Map workflows across administrative units</li>
<li>Standardize recurring approval steps</li>
<li>Reduce manual handoffs where possible</li>
</ul>

<h2>Skills Demonstrated</h2>
<p>
Administrative workflow analysis, process review,
institutional operations assessment, and documentation.
